{
  "stem": "1733.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were working with civilian engineers in stone quarries.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we had absolutely no contact with them at all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were not sustained with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not-- they were not-- they were not-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, they were just, we were just labor there for them, forced labor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the fences.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The fences-- and the-- the fences-- the camp was surrounded by fences, with the dogs on the outside of the fence.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We heard the barkings, and the towers-- the towers that were lit up at night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were happy when we were in the barracks and they left us alone, because we knew when we-- when we had to get up in the morning, when they were raus, raus, raus, they were beating us to get out of there, to get out of the barracks in a hurry and hurry fast by the kapos to line up for the SS when the SS came.",
      "word_count": 69
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sometimes it took a couple of hours for them to come, but we were standing outside and huddling in the cold.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They did not make any selections in Ohrdruf.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, they only took away the people that wouldn't work anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took them away from camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, people were sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They couldn't work anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They put them in-- they put them in the hospital area and the sick room.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And from there, they took them away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only a men's camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, nothing--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Nothing really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were just talking about ourselves, that we shouldn't give up hope.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the war is going to come to an end, and this is not going to-- you know, they're not going to be able to accomplish what they want to accomplish.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We did not know about the crematoria.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
